  <ThingDef ParentName="BasePawn" Name="MOL_BaseGolem">
    <defName>MOL_Golem_Iron</defName>
    <label>Iron Golem</label>
    <description>Raw iron ore achieving temporary autonomy through violent disturbance. Drilling, explosions, or seismic activity combined with ambient psychic phenomena can grant crude mobility and aggression to natural ore deposits.\n\nThe formation perceives threats and attacks with grinding, uncoordinated strikes until the animation exhausts itself. Iron animates readily but clumsily compared to other metals.\n\nMost attribute the underlying phenomena to archotech activity from ancient conflicts, though whether this was intentional design, collateral damage, or unintended consequence remains unknown.</description>
